A similar problem is examined [here][1], in which the solution hinges on the data sort order. Looking at [`LineChart`][2], [`SortingPolicy.NONE`][3] specifies &quot;The data should be left in the order defined by the list in `XYChart.dataProperty()`.&quot;

&gt;I had to change chart from my `SmoothChart` to standard `LineChart`.

Depending on your approach to smoothing, you may encounter the kind of cubic spline artifacts examined [here][4], which also occurs in [tag:jfreechart-fx]. An approach using B&#233;zier curves is adduced [here][5].

As tested using [synthetic data][6]:

